message.content:
Happy to help. What would you like to focus on? Here are quick options you can choose from, or tell me your goal and I’ll tailor it:

- Get something done now (3-step micro-plan)
  1) Pick one important task
  2) Work for 25 minutes (Pomodoro)
  3) Review what you did and decide next step

- Learn something new (short plan)
  1) Pick a topic
  2) Do a 20-minute mini-lesson or tutorial
  3) Do one quick practice problem or summary

- Boost well-being (quick routine)
  1) 5 minutes of deep breathing
  2) 5 minutes of light stretching or a short walk
  3) 2-minute reflection on how you feel

- Organize tasks (next actions)
  1) List top 3 priorities
  2) Break each into next concrete action
  3) Schedule or set reminders

- Creative / fun prompt
  1) Try a 10-minute creative exercise (short story, sketch, idea sprint)
  2) Share or summarize your result

Tell me which option fits, or share your goal (time you have, topic, constraints), and I’ll tailor a plan.
